{"tid":90651,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"EXCEL 時間轉換問題 高手請進","createTime":"2017-01-22T09:17:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-23T03:27:18.000Z","uid":38734,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bae73710bc5bdb796a5ed43403915fac88624de2","tid":90651,"uid":38734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T09:17:05.000Z","msg":"求幫手<br />\n返工要計糧 需要時間上ge轉換 <br />\n<br />\n我首先將excel入面ge cell set左做時:分:秒 e.g. 00:01:00 咁<br />\n想問下點樣可以整到以下的 custom round:<br />\n<br />\n我想個時間只會SHOW到 答正00或30分<br />\n***我想將00分至15分會當作 00分, 16分至45分都係當30分<br />\ne.g. 17:14 = 17:00,  16:45=16:30<br />\n<br />\n而46至59分就會當作最接近ge 小時 <br />\ne.g. 14:46 = 15:00, 17:59= 18:00<br />\n<br />\n想問條式係點?<br />\n<br />\n我試過上網睇 見到有mround條式 可以round 去最接近的30分鍾 但係45分到15分佢會自己ROUND UP左去 30 e.g. 15:45--&gt; 16:00  而唔係我想要ge 15:30<br />\ne.g. 15:15 佢會自己ROUND左去15:30 而唔係我想要ge 15:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無高手可以教教 謝謝"},{"pid":"caaeb37b1eb0bd6a764b6de8e8f92d3eb9e4e449","tid":90651,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:23:22.000Z","msg":"即係得15同45錯?"},{"pid":"c233f7b3e14f294a27afa6aad7b40beefc63dbba","tid":90651,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:28:01.000Z","msg":"用if得唔得呀？"},{"pid":"9b46b081a3d660373d1846706cbd84066ae2894a","tid":90651,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:42:44.000Z","msg":"當你資料係a1<br />\n你本身係咪打 =mround(a1,1/48)<br />\n你試下打 =mround(a1-1/1440,1/48)"},{"pid":"aff417fbd7b5f9611a0d2dafd7d60674c510eb75","tid":90651,"uid":38734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T13:51:20.000Z","msg":"Thanks 用左if 成功左 if 入面再set or OR 條件成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee1b1b403cf891f59dbfd34173536f8da2b4d296","tid":90651,"uid":21732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T22:23:02.000Z","msg":"入時同分再vlookup 一個table 都得"},{"pid":"0d184fa98b3a62f554493a6bf1b6334ef